    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i already checked my glucose and it's actually pretty high right now, like 180. if i take any insulin at all when i haven't eaten much i feel like i'm just asking for a crash in the middle of the night. wouldn't it be more logical to just hold off until tomorrow morning when i actually have breakfast? at least then i'm not risking a hypoglycemic episode while i'm asleep.",
